node.title: Triple shooting leaves two dead and one injured in Tasmania
node.alt: Flashing lights on Tasmania Police car with unidentified officer nearby.
node.description: Two people are dead, and another is wounded, following a shooting inÂ Tasmania's north-west.
node.content: ["Two people are dead, and another is wounded, following a shooting in Tasmania's north-west.", "Police officers were called to a Devonport house at about 1am on Saturday after receiving reports of gun shots.", "They found one dead man inside the house, while a second wounded man died a short time later.", "A woman found wounded outside the house is in hospital.", "In a statement, police said early investigations indicated the dead man was the alleged shooter, and that he knew both his victims.\u00a0", "Police said the firearm used in the shooting was recovered at the scene, and that there was no further concern for community safety.\u00a0", "The condition of the woman remains unclear.", "Two children who were at the property at the time of the shooting were not injured, but have been transported to the Launceston General Hospital as a precaution.\u00a0", "Detective Inspector Kim Steven will hold a media conference about the shooting at 11am in Devonport.", "Police have asked people to stay away from the William Street area while investigations continue.\u00a0"]
